Class AbstractDependencyVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nuxeo.build.maven.graph.AbstractDependencyVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.aether.graph.DependencyVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FlatPrinterDependencyVisitor, TreePrinterDependencyVisitor

    public abstract class AbstractDependencyVisitor
extends Object
implements org.eclipse.aether.graph.DependencyVisitor
    Prints the graph while traversing it. Do not print nodes provided through addIgnores(Collection). Inspired from AbstractDepthFirstNodeListGenerator
    Since:
    2.0
